text: King [[Boranel|Boranel ir'Wynarn]] of [[Breland]]'s youngest daughter, Princess Brela has inherited her father's quick wit and love of adventure. She loves to ride and hunt, and prefers [[Castle Arakhain]] to [[Wroat]]. Many says that she is the best of Boranelâ€™s brood still living, but she has no desire to ever wear the crown. She is fond of grand spectacles, and expects her upcoming twentieth birthday (which shares a date with [[Boldrei's Feast]]) to be a legendary event.
title: Brela ir'Wynarn
